   (ICRAI), Guangzhou, PEOPLES R CHINA, NOV 17-19, 2018},
Abstract = {The development of Human Action Recognition (HAR) system is getting
   popular. This project developed a HAR system for the application in the
   surveillance system to minimize the man-power for providing security to
   the citizens such as public safety and crime prevention. In this
   research, deep learning network using Recurrent Neural Network (RNN)
   with Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) are used to analyze dynamic video
   motion of sport actions and classify different types of actions and
   their performance. It could classify different types of human motion
   with a small number of video frame for efficiency and memory saving. The
   current accuracy achieved is up to 92.9\% but with high potential of
   further improvement.},
