Volume = {7},
Number = {4, SI},
Pages = {72-86},
Month = {OCT-DEC},
Abstract = {Today, Big Data is being leveraged in many industries from criminal
   justice to health care to real estate with powerful outcomes.
   Organizations are using Big Data to predict the future in turn making
   them smarter and efficient. All the health care data such as discharge
   and transfer patient data maintained in Computer based Patient Records
   (CPR), Personal Health Information (PHI), and Electronic Health Records
   (EHR). The use of Big Data analytics is becoming increasingly popular at
   health care centres, in clinical research, and consumer based medical
   product development. The biggest challenge with implementation of big
   data is that the nature of information of public health sector is of
   very sensitive nature and needs to be protected from unauthorized access
   and release of contents. Therefore, to provide solution to the
   deidentifying personal health big data in this paper we author make use
   of only mapper job framework for data encryption.},
